- produced: 6 improvements across 7 files: KpiCard trend indicators (all 5 Dashboard KPIs), Analytics Revenue Forecast + CPM Efficiency (2 new chart sections), Campaigns budget utilization bars, Bookings today-line Gantt marker, Login one-click auto-login. Build clean, dist deployed to public/demos/adverteyes/.
- decisions: Used existing AreaChart (dual-series) for forecast instead of ComposedChart to avoid new imports; TODAY_PCT computed at module level (stable across renders); budget bar color thresholds are 40/80%; credential quick-login falls back gracefully on API offline
